        Constructs a new zone
        Parameters:
        mode - The zone mode to apply
        vertices - A set of vertices, describing the polygon. Must be in consistent order (clockwise OR counterclockwise), with all elements unique.
        Throws:
        DegeneratePolygonException - If the polygon is degenerate (duplicate vertices, or zero area). This is not thrown for self-intersecting polygons with a well-defined interior (as per odd-even rule). However, undefined behavior may result from use of such polygons.
